{
  "stem": "11722.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were-- came to a-- through a village, I remember, about maybe two, three hours after we left the camp, middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We turned the corner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The guard hasn't turned the corner yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had a blanket with me, a rolled up blanket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I threw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My friend and I, three others, ran off the road into this yard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a fence, snow knee-deep, jumped over the fence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "These three after us, these three guys, these three inmates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "By that time, the guard turned the corner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He hollered, halt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Stop.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But there was no stopping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We ran.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They opened up fire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Those three never made it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember this other kid who was about 18-- I was 15-- crawled in the snow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We zigged and zagged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The bullets were flying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was woods-- a forest nearby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had to go across a little creek that was frozen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My-- my friend got hit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "A bullet grazed his ankle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were hiding out in these woods, a 15-year-old, an 18-year-old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Didn't know which way to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[SIGHS] There were some skeletons, you know, like, achtung.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Mines, whatever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were-- in the woods we found a-- a cottage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was like a-- it must've been a resort, because there was something like a motel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It had rooms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it had, I remember, it had a bomb shelter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we were looking for footprints.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were sniffing for humans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were like animals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We threw pebbles at these shutters to see whether anybody is around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we finally convinced nobody was around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We went in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We found pieces of frozen bread, some sack of sugar, some frozen potatoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was nourishment.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
